title: NFL ATL: Week 5 preview, Ross Tucker
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 5 preview, Ross Tucker
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling preview all of the Week 5 action and welcome in Ross Tucker from Sirius XM NFL Radio. The guys also defend their hero picks and recap the “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Buffalo Bills and Cleveland Browns. Find out if they believe Wesseling is close to eating his softball pants. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
